[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m938[0m[34m of [0m[33m1193[0m[31m ]--[0m

[30;1m526 | [0m[35male up. For this, a target tracking policy will be attached to the scaling target for your service w[0m
[30;1m527 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m528 | [0m[35mYou can configure auto scaling based on SQS Queue for your service as follows:[0m
[30;1m529 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m530 | [0m[35m```python[0m

[30;1m307 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m308 | [0m[35mThis `ServiceExtension` can now be reused and added to any number of different[0m
[30;1m309 | [0m[35mservice descriptions. This allows you to develop reusable bits of configuration,[0m
[30;1m310 | [0m[35mattach them to many different services, and centrally manage them. Updating the[0m
[30;1m311 | [0m[35m`ServiceExtension` in one place would update all services that use it, instead of[0m
[30;1m312 | [0m[35mrequiring decentralized updates to many different services.[0m
